<template>
  <v-card
      class="mx-auto"
      max-width="800"
      height="400"
      margin="auto"
      color="#1b5e20"
  >



        <v-sheet width="300" class="mx-auto">
          <v-form @submit.prevent>
            <v-card-text>
              <v-container class="check">
                <v-checkbox label="Botaniste"></v-checkbox>
                <v-checkbox label="Utilisateur"></v-checkbox>
              </v-container>
            </v-card-text>
            <v-text-field
                v-model="firstName"
                :rules="rules"
                label="First name"
            ></v-text-field>

            <v-file-input class="img"
                          label="File input"
                          variant="filled"
                          prepend-icon="mdi-camera"
            ></v-file-input>
            <v-textarea label="Label" variant="solo" class="text"></v-textarea>
            <v-btn type="submit" block class="mt-2">Submit</v-btn>
          </v-form>
        </v-sheet>




  </v-card>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name:"DemandeGardinnage",

}
</script>
<style>
.mx-auto{
  color:white;

  margin-top: 100px;
}



</style>
